/* IS.DISBURSEMENT is the application to define and execute Disbursement of AA contracts.

The AA contracts which are initiated as finance for an Islamic Contract might require a disbursement accompanying Customer contribution during each of the Payments made to the Vendor. To achieve this, the application IS.DISBURSEMENT receives the contribution details and the respective action is performed on the AA contract as Disbursement, Repayment or Commitment Decrease. */
